      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) with documented QA history; custom hemolysis post-processor subject to unit testing of core scalar integration routines.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is a commercially validated solver with ISO 9001-compliant QA documentation. The custom Python hemolysis post-processor was subjected to unit tests covering the Giersiepen power-law integration under standard operating conditions. Version control (Git, tag v3.1.0) is applied to all custom scripts. The batch orchestration layer managing the parallel parametric sweep was reviewed for correct job-dependency ordering. All validation runs executed to nominal completion with no reported runtime exceptions in the job scheduler logs."
