      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent spatial discretization verified against lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmarks confirming second-order accuracy. The hemolysis scalar transport equation was verified against an analytical solution for a simplified straight-tube geometry. All verification cases completed nominally with convergence to specified tolerances."
