      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated by residual reduction to 1e-5 or better for all governing equations; mass imbalance < 0.1%.",
      "rationale": "All production CFD runs achieved residual convergence to 1e-5 or better for continuity, momentum, and scalar transport equations. Global mass imbalance confirmed below 0.05% for all cases. The single operating point requiring relaxation factor adjustment (6 L/min / 4500 RPM) ultimately converged to the same residual threshold and is included in the assessed set. Iterative solver error is therefore bounded and within acceptable limits for MRL 2."
    },
