      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for centrifugal blood pump geometries (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2011). Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model selected as the regulatory-standard approach per FDA guidance. Model form uncertainty acknowledged as the dominant uncertainty source; sensitivity to power-law exponent documented in the uncertainty budget."
