    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. All validation runs completed nominally with residuals converging to specified tolerances. The CFD pipeline, comprising ANSYS Fluent 2022R2, the custom Python hemolysis post-processor, and the parametric sweep orchestration layer, performed without reported runtime failures across all validation cases. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 for all 5 operating points, satisfying the primary regulatory acceptance criterion. The credibility package is accepted as sufficient to support the Class II 510(k) submission for the CPB device hemolysis claim.",
